reviewText: I usually avoid my fave shows' "specials" like the plague. They never live up to expectations, they are obviously rushed into production to make a buck, etc.I took a chance on Red Green Christmas last year, and I was pleasantly surprised. It's very funny, well written, and just as good as the shows themselves. Wait until you see how Red takes holiday dinner to the relatives...If you love the show you won't be disappointed!

reviewText: Bought this sometime ago but just getting around to reviewing it.  I thought I had done it already.You have GOT to get this!  I saw the show and fell on the floor laughing.
